Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,請  法式吐司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好紅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.28,0:00:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,因為哥哥說午飯不帶了
